= Matrix Deformer =
#context: sop
#type: node

"""Deforms geometry by applying a transformation matrix derived from reference geometry."""

== Overview ==

Matrix Deformer computes the transformation matrix between a rest pose and a deformed pose, then applies that matrix to the input geometry. This allows geometry to follow the same deformation as a reference object without requiring a direct skin or blend shape relationship.

@inputs

Geometry to Deform:
    The geometry that will be deformed.

Rest:
    Rest-pose reference geometry.

Deformer:
    Deformed-pose reference geometry. The transform from Rest to Deformer is applied to the input.
